trVE.AposIdiomelon1.text = "Come, let us purify ourselves through almsgiving and works of mercy for the poor, not trumpeting, not publicizing our good deeds. Let not the left hand know what the right hand is doing; let not conceit scatter the fruit of almsgiving. Rather, let us call out in secret to the Knower of secrets: Father, forgive our trespasses, for You love mankind."
